    <item>
      <title>美国 12 月核心 CPI 涨幅低于预期，仅为 0.2%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-15/us-core-cpi-rises-less-than-forecast-in-december-at-0-2-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国 12 月份消费者物价有所回落，核心消费者物价指数继连续四个月上涨 0.3% 后，又上涨了 0.2%。迈克尔·麦基在彭博电视台上对这些数字进行了分析。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-15/us-core-cpi-rises-less-than-forecast-in-december-at-0-2-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 13:48:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韦德曼离职后，贝莱德提拔高管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/blackrock-promotes-senior-executives-amid-wiedman-s-departure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[曾被视为首席执行官拉里芬克 (Larry Fink) 潜在继任者的马克威德曼 (Mark Wiedman) 宣布离职后，贝莱德公司 (BlackRock Inc.) 正在擢升数名高管，以扩大其在美洲和主要机构客户的业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/blackrock-promotes-senior-executives-amid-wiedman-s-departure</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 11:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英伟达股价涨至 3 万亿美元，华尔街却不为所动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/nvda-nvidia-s-3-trillion-rally-is-on-edge-wall-street-is-unfazed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自 ChatGPT 帮助引发人工智能热潮以来的两年间，英伟达公司的市值增长了 3 万亿美元，这比历史上如此短时间内的任何一次股市上涨都要大。但对于这家芯片制造商来说，形势正在发生变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/nvda-nvidia-s-3-trillion-rally-is-on-edge-wall-street-is-unfazed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 10:17:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通胀缓解令市场平静，英国债券价格创 2023 年以来最大涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/pound-falls-as-uk-inflation-slowdown-opens-door-for-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府债券价格上涨，因为数据显示英国12月份通胀率下降，缓解了人们对今年困扰该国资产的持续价格压力的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/pound-falls-as-uk-inflation-slowdown-opens-door-for-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 07:21:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币受到科技股的追捧，相关性增强</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/bitcoin-btc-nasdaq-100-correlation-at-two-year-high-before-us-cpi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币与美国科技股指数之间的相关性已达到两年来的最高水平，因为周三股市对美国通胀数据的反应为数字代币奠定了更强劲的基调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/bitcoin-btc-nasdaq-100-correlation-at-two-year-high-before-us-cpi</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 01:36:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际能源署预计今年石油盈余将减少，油价小幅上涨至每桶 80 美元附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国对俄罗斯制裁的影响持续显现，且国际能源署 (International Energy Agency) 撤回对今年的看跌预测，油价突破每桶 80 美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-15</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 23:31:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储押注导致 CPI 数据公布，收益率下跌，股市飙升：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[通胀放缓增强了人们对美联储今年将有降息空间的预期，导致股市上涨、债券收益率随美元下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 22:42:48 GMT</pubDate>
